    <header class="chapter-hero">
        <div class="chapter-hero__badge">Chapter 5</div>
        <h1 class="chapter-hero__title">LLMs &amp; Transformers</h1>
        <p class="chapter-hero__subtitle">The attention revolution - from sequence models to large language models for civil engineering</p>
    </header>

    <section class="chapter-overview">
        <p>Transformers have revolutionized AI beyond NLP - from automated report generation to structural data analysis. Explore the attention mechanism, transformer architecture, GPT, BERT, and their civil engineering applications across 10 sub-chapters.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="sub-grid">
        <a href="sub1.html" class="sub-card">
            <div class="sub-card__icon teal"><i class="fa-solid fa-timeline"></i></div>
            <span class="sub-card__num">5.1</span>
            <div class="sub-card__title">Sequence Models & RNNs</div>
            <div class="sub-card__desc">Understanding sequential data - time series, text, and why order matters for sensor readings and documents.</div>
            <div class="sub-card__tags"><span class="sub-card__tag">RNN</span><span class="sub-card__tag">LSTM</span></div>
