            <div class="sub-card__desc">The breakthrough idea - learning what to focus on, just like an engineer prioritizes critical structural elements.</div>
            <div class="sub-card__tags"><span class="sub-card__tag">attention</span><span class="sub-card__tag">QKV</span></div>
        </a>
        <a href="sub3.html" class="sub-card">
