            <span class="sub-card__num">5.4</span>
            <div class="sub-card__title">BERT & Encoder Models</div>
            <div class="sub-card__desc">Bidirectional understanding - masked language modeling, fine-tuning for CE document classification.</div>
            <div class="sub-card__tags"><span class="sub-card__tag">BERT</span><span class="sub-card__tag">encoder</span></div>
        </a>
        <a href="sub5.html" class="sub-card">
